Name: Blue Zip-Up Hooded Cardigan-3 months
Description:
Tartine et Chocolat blue zip-up hooded cardigan features navy trim, a hood and long sleeves both featuring navy elbow patches. Additionally this cardigan features a thick navy stripe down the left hand side and at the reverse, two small pockets on the left side, branding just above the trim and a central zip fastening. Made from 92% cotton, 2% cashmere. Machine wash at 30 degrees.

This adorable blue hooded cardigan from Tartine et Chocolat is a must have item for your little boy's wardrobe this season. The blue and navy colours make this a classic piece which will go with almost anything you want to pair it with to make that perfect and stylish outfit for your young man. To complete the look team with these Burberry beige shorts and these Lacoste white and grey Europa velcro trainers.

These bright and vibrant socks from Tartine et Chocolate are perfect for your little girl's spring/summer wardrobe with the colouring being right on trend for this season. The adorable girly additions make these a simple must have that your angel is bound to fall in love with. Baby Graziella two-in-one features a blue knitted v-neck vest with a white and pale blue trim and an elasticated hem. In addition, this vest has the collar, two button fastenings and short sleeves of a linen shirt stitched to the neckline and cuffs to make a shirt and vest layered combination. Made from 100% cotton, dry clean only.

Cambridge and Oxford watch out! This vest from Baby Graziella has kickstarted the making of a preppy trend that will make him not only look adorable, but feel luxuriously comfortable in 100% cotton. Name: Sky blue Liddesdale Jacket-XL (12-13 years)
Description:
Barbour sky blue Liddesdale quilted jacket with a navy corduroy collar. Also features popper fastening running down the centre front, twin pockets at the hip with 'Barbour' embroidered at the left pocket, twin vents at the rear and and a zip fastening inner pocket. Made from 100% Polyamide, machine wash at 30 degree wash.

PLEASE NOTE, WE ARE UNABLE TO SHIP THIS DESIGNER TO COUNTRIES OUTSIDE OF THE UK.

Babour are famous for their legendary durability and country inspired style and this piece is no exception. The sky blue hue brings a fresh and contemporary edge to the authentic Liddesdale jacket, ensuring your little one cuts a dash in England's rolling country. Complete the look with the Wildfox 'ALL YOU NEED IS LOVE' tee and the Little Marc Jacobs Kourtney mid- wash slim fit jeans.

Milly Minis tweed jacket features a casual collar, long sleeves, six gold buttons on the front and two pockets with flaps. Made from 90% cotton and 10% polyamide. Dry clean only.

Elegantly cut and cropped, Milly Minis cream tweed jacket is a smart choice for work or play. The lightweight fabric makes this style ideal for warmer weather whilst the gold buttons add extra glitz and glamour to an already sartorial number. Description:
Milly Minis cherry pocket shift dress features a crew neckline, sleeveless design and twin pockets at the hips. Also has button fastenigs at the reverse and a graphic cream square design throughout. Made from 100% Silk, dry clean only.

This seriously chic dress from Milly Minis is perfect for the sartorially switched on. Combining two of this seasons biggest trends into one sophisticated dress the graphic and colour block design create a piece that even the most stylish of women would love to own. Name: Grey suit with black trim
Description:
Dior grey suit features trousers with a black trim, a clasp and zip fastening fly and an adjustable waistband. Additionally have a black lining and four pockets, the right reverse of which features a branded plaque. The grey suit jacket features a black trim, two button fastenings, three pockets and a stripe lining at the arms. Additionally have a black branded lining, button down cuffs and a Dior plaque above the left lower pocket. Made from 100% Wool, dry clean only.

Your little gent will be the pinnacle of sophistication when wearing this Dior suit. The dapper set are a hybrid of old school elegance and contemporary detailing, ensuring that he looks distinguished at special occasions. Complete the look with the Tommy Hilfiger stretch poplin smart shirt in white and the Junior Gaultier black and white striped tie.

Name: Grey Smart shortall
Description:
Dior grey smart shortall features button fastenings running down the centre front, a faux shirt insert with button fastenings, elasticated armholes, decorative pocket details at the hips, a 'Dior' tag at the left hip, a faux waistcoat detail at the reverse and popper fastenings at the crotch. Made form 100% Wool, dry clean only.

This incredibly smart shortall from Dior is perfect for special occasions and formal dressing. The suit style design will make him the most dapper baby at any event, whist the soft cotton lining will ensure he stays comfortable whilst he poses in this charming piece. Team with the Fendi Navy Logo Lace Up Trainers and the Timberland Grey Jersey Blazer to complete the look.

Name: Dressing Up Doll
Description:
Dior dressing up doll with three dresses. A moveable limbed doll measuring approximately 40cm tall and wearing a coral Dior dress and white shoes. Comes complete with two branded Dior dresses, mini cardboard hangers and matching belts for each dress. Presented in a Dior box with an interior that functions as a dolly dressing room. The box measures 41x36x14. Not suitable for children under three years.

Due to the dimensions of the Dior packaging, we are unable to giftwrap this item with an AlexandAlexa giftbox.

With her very own designer wardrobe, this dolly-about-town from Dior  will make a stylish companion for your little girl. If you like this, take a look at the Dior White Fluffy Rabbit and the Dior White And Pink Soft Doll
